content: It sounds like Hitarth Parikh had the opportunity to meet Saina Nehwal during his convocation ceremony. Saina Nehwal is a well-known Indian professional badminton player who has achieved great success in her career. She has held the world number one ranking in women's singles badminton and has won a total of 24 international titles, including ten Superseries titles. Her accomplishments in the sport have made her one of the most successful badminton players in India's history.
